data.description: Welcome to 901 Mclintock Cove, a charming 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom haven with dual living rooms, a study, and a media room. Outside, the lush lawn and privacy fence create an inviting outdoor space with a covered patio for relaxation. Inside, a spacious study beckons creativity, while the kitchen is a culinary masterpiece with granite countertops and stainless steel appliances. The main level also features a delightful living space blending the kitchen, dining room, and living room, illuminated by natural light. Resilient vinyl flooring adds elegance and practicality. The master bedroom, conveniently located downstairs, offers a spa-like retreat with a walk-in closet, deep soaker tub, separate tiled shower, and double vanity sinks. A laundry room and tasteful half bathroom cater to convenience and guests. Upstairs, three guest bedrooms provide ample space for family or friends. A second living room or game room promises hours of enjoyment, while a full bathroom ensures everyone's comfort. The pièce de résistance is the sprawling media room, perfect for movie nights and lasting memories. Additionally, a cozy nook off the game room offers a quiet spot for studying or reading. This enchanting home is a true masterpiece, best appreciated in person. Don't miss your chance to schedule a showing at 901 Mclintock Cove and embark on a magical journey to your happily ever after!
